br />\n<br />\n日日捱得好辛苦 真係好大壓力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我讀year 1 果時都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係時間係會過，依家睇返轉頭，果陣時嘅壓力真係好少事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到你出嚟做嘢之後就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望爸打你加油，唔好放棄喺外國讀書嘅機會，呢個係人生中非常重要嘅經驗同時光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  trust me"},{"pid":"aa7746ac1153230c0973eb4826b060b95612edc3","tid":17200,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>是咁的 讀緊外地大學yr1<br />\n就嚟完sem1 讀落發覺自己好似唔太適合個科<br />\n於是想返香港讀書 原本自己個分就唔多靚啦<br />\n就算入到U都一定入唔到想讀嘅科<br />\n所以打算返去讀hd/asso<br />\n但仲有小小矛盾好驚做錯決定 有冇quit過U嘅巴絲分享下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：未同老豆老母講</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第日你會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果法國呢科唔適合，可以讀埋 year 1 先，再睇吓轉唔轉到其他科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日日捱得好辛苦 真係好大壓力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我讀year 1 果時都係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係時間係會過，依家睇返轉頭，果陣時嘅壓力真係好少事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到你出嚟做嘢之後就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望爸打你加油，唔好放棄喺外國讀書嘅機會，呢個係人生中非常重要嘅經驗同時光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  trust me</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點都好 多謝巴打嘅意見先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169bbd650376dc527de9f95ab6b8a82ed94b9a73","tid":17200,"uid":1954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"你間大學冇得轉科？"},{"pid":"d368792c44dbbac22a58f9549baff70ab32c21e9","tid":17200,"uid":36126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"建議讀住先<br />\n了解多啲自己個科同時揾轉系資